headlines.headline: Decouple custom code to secure your core
headlines.text: Move extension code to a separate platform to decouple it from the digital core and profit from independent innovation cycles.

headlines.headline: Accelerate cloud transformation
headlines.text: Reuse ABAP assets and current ABAP developers with your business and application know-how to build breakthrough innovations in the cloud.

headlines.headline: Innovate without administration
headlines.text: Take advantage of latest ABAP, SAP HANA and  SAP Cloud Platform innovations while relying on SAP to manage infrastructure and operations.

headlines.headline: Extend SAP S/4HANA Cloud
headlines.text: Use a innovative ABAP stack with SAP HANA and reliable SAP Cloud Platform services to create and run custom extensions to SAP S/4HANA Cloud.
